                <button type="button" class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 shadow-md shadow-indigo-600/20 transition-all active:scale-95 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest" onclick="guardarUsuario()">Guardar Datos</button>
